verbose_text: Other PET- and PET/CT tracers have been introduced for diagnosing prostate carcinoma based on an increased androgen receptor expression ([18 F] fluorodihydrotestosterone (FDHT)), fatty acid synthesis ([11 C] acetate), amino acid transport and protein synthesis ([11 C] methionine) as well as choline turnover by [11 C]-/[18 F] labelled choline derivates XREF_BIBR - XREF_BIBR.
